    "Ma et al. [58] conducted a study on the proactive project scheduling problem and made use of a two-layer nested tabu search heuristic algorithm in their analysis.",
    "In addition to these efforts, several optimization techniques have been proposed to tackle project scheduling problems that involve uncertainty in project estimation."
